text: The Immortals () is a 1974 Romanian adventure movie directed by Sergiu Nicolaescu (who also stars) and starring Amza Pellea, Ion Besoiu, Ilarion Ciobanu, Jean Constantin, Gheorghe Dinică, Colea Răutu. == Other websites == * Category:1974 adventure movies Category:Romanian adventure movies Category:Movies directed by Sergiu Nicolaescu
title: The Immortals (1974 movie)
